entries.journal_entry_description: Tarand Crowe wants you to deliver a package of smuggled goods for him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Pick a portion of the spice plant that Maghr Scutu wants.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Collect the Spice Plant in the Atrium
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to return to the main level.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to Return to the Main Level
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Use the space terminal to launch into space.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Go to the rendezvous point and deliver the smuggled spice.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Maghr Scutu that you have failed.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Return to Maghr Scutu and Report your Failure
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: You have delivered the spice. Now, return to Tarand for your reward.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Land and Return to Tarand in the Cantina
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: You were rewarded 250 credits for your help.
